SIMPLE: unstudied
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unstudied
<hw>Unstudied</hw>  <def>See <er>studied</er>.</def>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unstudied
<hw>Un*stud"ied</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
studied; not acquired by study; unlabored; natural.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not skilled; unversed; -- followed by
<xex>in</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Not spent in study.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧To cloak the defects of their <xex>unstudied</xex> years.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 1582 -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsubstantial</ent>⟦br⟧
